                <note rend="inline" type="source">862.00/3283: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dodd</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-07-01T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 1, 1934—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>82. Your 124, June 30, 5 p.m. I should appreciate your sending a series of
                    frequent brief analytic telegrams during the current German crisis.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
